# Summary
This documentation page describes the Braze integration with Amplitude, enabling bidirectional data flow including sending cohorts to Braze for targeted marketing, streaming events from Amplitude to Braze in real-time, and sending Braze events back to Amplitude via Braze Currents for comprehensive analytics.

